this hall. This essay analyses the stele inscription, historical resources and objects remained today, and examines the historical development of Fachuan Hall. The conclusion confirms the dating of Fachuan Hall when Liang Sicheng came to Zhengding in 1933 and shows more details about this hall and the Buddhist statues in it.</note></biblStruct><bibl type="formatted" subtype="bibliography" resp="https://www.zotero.org/styles/chicago-note-bibliography-17th-edition">
